    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. GCI of 2.1% exceeds the required threshold for discretization error. Normalized RMS error of 8.3% for RH index is within acceptable bounds. Six factors not assessed are consistent with MRL 2 scope per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
